.DS_Store
._*

# --- Design files ---
docs/

# --- Submodules ---
# When you add a submodule, git records the pinned commit in the
# .gitmodules file. The actual submodule working tree is ignored
# at the parent level (it's tracked inside the submodule's own repo).
